    "summary": "I started in 1994 my own business in training and supporting organizations in their change and improvement projects by developing, executing and selling custom made training programs for business development in the fields of After-Sales, Sales, Management and leadership. For measurement we work with KPI\u2019s that work in daily business. \n\nMy role is: Owner of VTI Benelux B.V., Senior Trainer and Performance Consultant\n\nThe markets I work for are Technical Service Providers, Oil & Gas industry, Automotive, Motorcycles, Trucks, Agriculture, their suppliers and their dealer channels.\n.\nI work for customers in The Netherlands, Belgium, Luxembourg, Germany, Austria, Switzerland, The UK, The USA, South Africa, Angola and Russia. \n\nIncreasing dealer/business performance on all levels, dealer/business development and change management on no nonsense base and with the right balance between facts and people is one of my specialties\n \nBefore starting my own company I worked 3 years as managing director in the technical service industry and 10 years as Business Manager in the Industrial automation active in the fields of CAD/CAM, CAE and production logistics. In these jobs I was responsible for improvement of business results and increasing market share.\n\n\nSpecialties:\t\nTraining Development en Training delivery\n\t\t\tIntegration of sales and after-sales\n\t\t\tPerformance Consulting\n\t\t\tDealer management\n\t\t\tWorkshop management\n\t\t\tBusiness development",
